fields.character_bio:
The Boy Who Lived
The Boy Who Returned

A young boy who dreamed of being a pirate. He ate the Gomu-Gomu Devil fruit which turned him in to a 'Rubber Man' and gave him super stretching abilities. All Devil fruit users are unable to swim and lose their powers in the sea. As he makes his way across the Grand Line, the infamous sea of adventure he builds a crew of companions named the 'Straw Hat Pirates', named after the straw hat he wears,  a gift from his childhood idol.
fields.quote: I'm gonna be king of the pirates!

fields.character_bio: in a world where everyone has a quirk (a superpower) Midoriya Izuku, a quirkless teenage inherits the quirk of his idol, the number one hero All Might. with this new ability he aims for the top of the hero-led society, as the new symbol of peace
